  <li><strong>Level 3 Building Survey:</strong> A comprehensive survey suitable for older, extended or altered properties needing detailed insight.</li>
  <li><strong>Damp &amp; Timber Inspections:</strong> Get expert advice on damp, mould, or timber decay, with practical next steps.</li>
  <li><strong>Floorplans &amp; Measured Surveys:</strong> Useful for renovation, marketing or compliance.</li>
  <li><strong>Ventilation Reports:</strong> Identify airflow issues contributing to condensation or poor indoor air quality.</li>
